  "text": "It has been determined that obesity and overweightness have been associated with an increased risk of the cancers of the esophagus, colorectal, breast, endometri-al and kidney (4). Datta and Biswas showed that breast cancer is most common in women with BMI more than 30 [CITATION_1] .",
